Package exceptions

Exception Summary
AlreadyLoggedInException Exception to be thrown when logged in user attempts to log in again.
CommandNonExistant Exception for handling improperly formatted or non-existant commands.
IncorrectArgumentType Exception for handling commands that are not passed the correct type of arguments.
IncorrectNumberOfArguments Exception for handling commands that are not passed the correct number of arguments.
InvalidTopicException Exception for handling operations performed on null or invalid topics.
InvalidUserException  
UserNotLoggedInException Exception for handling attempts at operations that require authentication, where the user is not authenticated.
